### **1. The HTML Structure (`index.html`)**
This structure uses semantic `<article>` tags for the cards and a `<button>` for the fixed action.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Responsive Card Layout</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <main class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Our Premium Services</h1>
        </header>

        <div class="card-wrapper">
            <article class="card">
                <div class="card-image"></div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Web Development</h3>
                    <p>Build high-performance, scalable web applications with the latest tech stacks.</p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
                <div class="card-image"></div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>
                    <p>Create intuitive and beautiful user interfaces that drive engagement and growth.</p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
                <div class="card-image"></div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Cloud DevOps</h3>
                    <p>Optimize your deployment pipeline with robust cloud infrastructure solutions.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </main>

    <button class="fixed-btn">Help & Support</button>

</body>
</html>
```

---

### **2. The CSS Styles (`style.css`)**

```css
/* 1. Global Reset & Box Sizing */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box; /* Padding/Borders stay inside the width */
}

body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f4f7f6;
    padding: 20px;
    color: #333;
}

/* 2. Container Layout */
.container {
    max-width: 100%; /* Default for Mobile */
    margin: 0 auto;
}

header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

/* 3. Card Styling (Box Model) */
.card-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column; /* Mobile: Stacked layout */
    gap: 20px;
}

.card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;   /* Border */
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;            /* Padding */
    margin-bottom: 10px;      /* Margin */
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.card-image {
    height: 150px;
    background-color: #3498db;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

.card-content h3 {
    margin: 15px 0 10px;
}

/* 4. Media Queries for Responsiveness */

/* Tablet View: Two Columns */
@media (min-width: 600px) {
    .card-wrapper {
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .card {
        flex: 0 1 calc(50% - 10px); /* Takes 50% width minus gap */
    }
}

/* Desktop View: Centered with Max-Width */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
        max-width: 1100px; /* Centered Layout */
    }
    .card {
        flex: 1; /* Three equal columns */
    }
}

/* 5. Fixed Positioning */
.fixed-btn {
    position: fixed;     /* Stuck to viewport */
    bottom: 20px;        /* 20px from bottom edge */
    right: 20px;         /* 20px from right edge */
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: #2c3e50;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 30px;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 1000;       /* Ensure it stays on top */
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.fixed-btn:hover {
    background-color: #e67e22;
}
```

